name: Sam Jones
values: Honesty, openness, mutual respect and understanding

summary: Sam Jones is a non-binary 36-year-old, tech-savvy software engineer. They are 6'2", hold a doctoral degree from Harvard University, and are open to dating people of the same or other genders. They currently live in Los Angeles, but are originally from Seattle. Sam speaks English, Spanish, and Mandarin fluently. They are agnostic, lean liberal in politics, and is seeking a life partner for a monogamous relationship. Sam enjoys biking, painting, reading literary fiction, and playing chess. They own a dog, have no children, but they're open to having kids in the future. Sam's dating preferences include potential partners aged between 30 and 40, who lead an active lifestyle and enjoys a good drink.
